    "license": "Data sourced from public ODEJ Bejaia website. Verify before production use.",
    "notes": [
      "Phone numbers reconstructed from the site's RTL display order (e.g. '36,49,33,(034)' -> '034 33 49 36'). Same digits, un-reversed.",
      "GPS coordinates are NOT published on the source site. 'coordinates' is null for every entry and MUST be geocoded at commune level before mapping. Do not invent exact coordinates.",
      "activity_tags are derived from each category's official 'missions' text on the site, not assigned arbitrarily.",
      "data_quality_flags capture inconsistencies present on the source (shared emails, missing fields). Values are preserved as-found, not corrected by guessing.",
      "The 'events' array is intentionally empty: the source site has no structured event feed. Events are created via the admin dashboard. Any demo events must be clearly labelled as samples."
    ]
  },
